                <div class="mb-4"><a href="/External.aspx?u=https://www.hcltech.com/HCLforEquality" target="_blank">
                    <img src="https://internationalwomensday.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/home/hcl/HCL-IWD2021-herobanner.jpg" alt="HCL" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block" />
